firecracker-containerd (0.1.0-1) trixie; urgency=medium

  * Initial release for Mikrom platform
  * Includes firecracker-containerd daemon
  * Includes firecracker-agent binary
  * systemd service file for automatic startup
  * CNI plugins for VM networking
  * Default configuration with devmapper snapshotter
  * Integration with mikrom-agent via containerd socket

